      "MedicationRequest?code=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|5521,http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|8640,http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|6851,http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|1256,http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|265323",
